Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: DLF Prime Tower is a commercial building in the Industrial Sector of Okhla Phase I. It is one of the Grade A commercial developments in Okhla and is within 3.7 km from Govindpuri Metro Station. There are 5-star hotels as well as hospitals and malls within a 2-5 km radius and good connectivity by road and metro to all the major micro-markets of Delhi NCR.
